OL,3,CGaza boy tells of miracle survival
OL,4,Cafter losing leg in blast
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent Lucy Watson met
OL,7,Fwith 12 year-old Abdallah Kehil whose
OL,8,Fleg was saved from amputation after a
OL,9,Frocket landed in front of his school.
OL,10,FHe continues with bravery and
OL,11,Fundiminished dreams to become a model.
OL,13,FThe war in Gaza has continued for
OL,14,Fnearly 11 months, and throughout that
OL,15,Ftime we have heard often about how it
OL,16,Fhas affected its children - who make
OL,17,Fup half of the territory's population.
OL,19,FThey are experiencing death and
OL,20,Fdestruction daily, and quite often,
OL,21,Fwitnessing the unimaginable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
