OL,3,CGaza boy tells of miracle survival
OL,4,Cafter losing leg in blast
OL,6,FRecently, I went to Egypt to report on
OL,7,Fdesperately ill Palestinians who,
OL,8,Funtil May, were allowed to leave Gaza
OL,9,Fto go to Egypt, and elsewhere, for
OL,10,Fmedical treatment.
OL,12,FOn our last day of filming in Cairo,
OL,13,Fwe were at the Nasser Institute
OL,14,FHospital talking to cancer patients
OL,15,Fand their doctors.
OL,17,FThroughout the day, unbeknownst to us,
OL,18,Fwe were being watched. It was only
OL,19,Fwhen we started to pack up did the
OL,20,Fcurious 12 year old observer make
OL,21,Fhimself known.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
