OL,3,CGaza boy tells of miracle survival
OL,4,Cafter losing leg in blast
OL,6,FHis name was Abdallah Kehil, and his
OL,7,Fresilience and bravery astounded us,
OL,8,Fbut not only us, the Egyptian
OL,9,Fpresident too.
OL,11,FAs he moved along the corridors of the
OL,12,Fhospital ward in his wheelchair,
OL,13,FAbdallah had an undeniable popularity
OL,14,Fand presence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
