OL,3,CGaza boy tells of miracle survival
OL,4,Cafter losing leg in blast
OL,6,FThe other children adored him. He
OL,7,Fsmiled often and they followed him
OL,8,Flike the Pied Piper. But, Abdallah's
OL,9,Fsmile hid horrors no 12 year old
OL,10,Fshould ever see. He wanted to share
OL,11,Fhis own story, about a school day in
OL,12,FNovember.
OL,14,F"We were bombed, a rocket hit us in
OL,15,Ffront of our school," he said.
OL,17,F"We were sitting down and suddenly the
OL,18,Fmissile struck us. My leg was blown
OL,19,Foff. My friends' bodies were
OL,20,Fscattered."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
