OL,3,CGaza boy tells of miracle survival
OL,4,Cafter losing leg in blast
OL,6,FAbdallah crawled along the ground away
OL,7,Ffrom the devastation. Medics found him
OL,8,Fand carried him to hospital where he
OL,9,Fhad to fight for his own life. He'd
OL,10,Flost every one of his friends.
OL,12,FOnce his condition stabilised, he made
OL,13,Fa video from his hospital bed in Gaza
OL,14,Fand put it online, asking the Egyptian
OL,15,Fpresident to save his leg.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
