OL,3,CGaza boy tells of miracle survival
OL,4,Cafter losing leg in blast
OL,6,FJust days later, Abdallah and his mum
OL,7,Fwere rescued. Their evacuation was
OL,8,Fshown on Egyptian state television, as
OL,9,Fhe was moved from ambulance to
OL,10,Fambulance, hospital to hospital, until
OL,11,Fhe reached Cairo, and the Nasser
OL,12,FInstitute, where surgeons were waiting.
OL,14,FHe explained to me what they did to
OL,15,Ffix his leg.
OL,17,F"They took a muscle from my back and
OL,18,Fskin from my thigh, to repair my other
OL,19,Fleg. They put it back together as
OL,20,Fnew," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
