OL,3,CGaza boy tells of miracle survival
OL,4,Cafter losing leg in blast
OL,6,FIn January, he was invited by
OL,7,FPresident Abdul Fattah El Sisi to a
OL,8,Fnational event at Cairo's New Capital
OL,9,FTheatre. It was there - on stage -
OL,10,Fthat Abdallah said to the audience, "I
OL,11,Fwish I could hug the President."
OL,13,FAt that point, El Sisi walked up on
OL,14,Fstage and hugged him. His survival
OL,15,Fdefies belief, but so too does his
OL,16,Fspirit.
