OL,6,F"We are strong. We're brave. We are
OL,7,Fnot afraid," he said.
OL,9,FI am famous now, he said to me.
OL,10,FAbdallah is indeed famous, but he
OL,11,Fplans to be more so.
OL,13,FHe will walk again and wants to be a
OL,14,Fmodel and, having faced what he's
OL,15,Ffaced and overcome it, few can doubt
OL,16,Fhim.
